Human Connectome Project data-use acknowledgement
==================================================

The diffusion MRI example slices in this directory (coronal_3T.nii.gz,
coronal_7T.nii.gz and the associated masks, T1w underlays, bvals and bvecs) are
derived from a single coronal slice of HCP subject 191841 (within-subject 3T and
7T diffusion acquisitions), resampled to the subject's ACPC/T1w anatomical frame.

Data were provided in part by the Human Connectome Project, WU-Minn Consortium
(Principal Investigators: David Van Essen and Kamil Ugurbil; 1U54MH091657) funded
by the 16 NIH Institutes and Centers that support the NIH Blueprint for
Neuroscience Research; and by the McDonnell Center for Systems Neuroscience at
Washington University.

Any work using these slices must acknowledge the HCP as above and abide by the
HCP Open Access Data Use Terms (https://www.humanconnectome.org/study/hcp-young-adult/data-use-terms).
